{"tid":555912,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"街邊小食腸粉果啲醬係邊到有得買？","createTime":"2018-02-10T03:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T05:05:49.000Z","uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43429be90157e87254ba47dcc79c98f0d1cdaa70","tid":555912,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"平時食開一檔腸粉燒賣啲醬好好味，不過好貴，日日食唔係辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過自己整，但啲味好唔同<br />\n平時講開嘅豉油，應該唔係生抽嚟？我試過落生抽好似太過鹹，街邊果啲好似稀啲，多少少水？<br />\n跟住所謂甜醬，落超巿買好似係叫海鮮醬？落過好似又係唔岩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻醬應該就真係麻醬，係唔同牌子咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有自己整開啲醬，邊到買、咩牌子嘅好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"191f180bf83987c2ecca01264804d73f29f82572","tid":555912,"uid":21423,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3940b846818adae2c6aafa8e00ba73dac7dc34f","tid":555912,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"淘寶買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926c28be40e2fbdb5ada34833b97968388c4c677","tid":555912,"uid":73750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"甜醬麻醬豉油加芝麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac28c27e7308417a431a267c1f3f0074ac53fac2","tid":555912,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93391fdf2b334769ad46b40c4d8be7dce4c9f4ab","tid":555912,"uid":31920,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食粉果要落咩醬？頂多豉油咪得</blockquote><br />\n有無食埋蘋果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉粿呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369